reviewText: I am a big fan of the 1960's animation of technical imagination.  This 5 episode DVD satisfies my need for this early adventure.  The video quality is poor and the audio is fair.  It reminds me of a Betamax recording.  I wish it was a more professional quality product but I got what I wanted.  A few episodes of this series.

Got this for my Brother as a Christmas gift...like a lot of "Boomers" he has a great love for these classic cartoons and he had been watching them on YouTube.  He tells me the reproduction quality is excellent and now he can enjoy is favorite childhood cartoon anytime!
